OL,3,CHalifax worker sentenced for stealing
OL,4,Cthousands to fund gambling addiction
OL,6,FA bank worker who stole #12,000 from
OL,7,Fcustomers' accounts has been given 180
OL,8,Fhours of community service.
OL,10,FJan Olivier, 49, took the money while
OL,11,Fhe worked at Halifax in Poole, Dorset.
OL,13,FIt was claimed in court that Olivier,
OL,14,Fwho had worked at the bank for 17
OL,15,Fyears, had a gambling addiction and
OL,16,Fhuge debts.
OL,18,FThe alarm was raised when the family
OL,19,Fof one of the victims noticed money
OL,20,Fwas missing after the great
OL,21,Fgrandfather had died.
