OL,6,FEdward Teggin, 89, died in June 2022,
OL,7,Fa few days after being knocked down by
OL,8,Fa careless driver at a junction in
OL,9,FPoole.
OL,11,FAn investigation began after his
OL,12,Ffamily queried a transfer of #9,000 at
OL,13,Fthe bank a couple of months earlier.
OL,15,FThree further cases of fraud were
OL,16,Funcovered.
OL,18,FThe judge told Olivier that he had
OL,19,Fabused his position of trust by
OL,20,Ftargeting the old and vulnerable.
