OL,6,FEdward Teggin's daughter says he
OL,7,Fshould have been sent to prison.
OL,9,F"There is no justice at all. I think
OL,10,Fit should have been harsher especially
OL,11,Fas it was all elderly people it
OL,12,Faffected," said Jackie Greenslade.
OL,14,FJackie was tearful when she read her
OL,15,Fimpact statement to the court.
OL,17,FShe said: "I'd have liked them to have
OL,18,Fthrown the book at him, and for him to
OL,19,Fhave had time in prison to think about
OL,20,Fwhat he's done to elderly people."
